en_160442_0	One person has died by colliding with a bus in Pidurangala area in Sigiriya.
en_160442_1	The accident has taken place at about 2.15am in the early morning.
en_160442_2	This person has been on his way back home from the UNP May Rally held in Cambel Grounds and he has slipped from the footboard and the bus has run over over him.
en_160442_3	He has been admitted to the Dambulla hospital and later has died.
en_160442_4	The deceased is a 44 year-old resident in New Village in Sigiriya.
